410
00:22:34,625 --> 00:22:39,208
♪ AND I KNOW IT'S TIME TO FLY ♪

411
00:22:39,291 --> 00:22:42,500
♪ AND LIKE THE WIND
WE WILL RUN ♪

412
00:22:42,583 --> 00:22:44,583
♪ THROUGH THESE SKIES ON HIGH ♪

413
00:22:44,666 --> 00:22:47,125
♪ WITH OUR GOAL IN SIGHT ♪

414
00:22:47,208 --> 00:22:50,166
♪ WE WILL RUN
WITH ALL OUR MIGHT ♪

415
00:22:50,250 --> 00:22:55,416
♪ TOMORROW AND TODAY
WILL NEVER EVER PASS US BY ♪

416
00:22:55,500 --> 00:22:58,083
♪ WE WILL NOT STOP NOW ♪

417
00:22:58,166 --> 00:23:01,000
♪ KEEP YOUR HEART ALIVE
AND YOUR DREAM SURVIVES ♪

418
00:23:01,083 --> 00:23:05,000
♪ AND YOU CROSS
THE FINISH LINE ♪

419
00:23:05,083 --> 00:23:06,750
♪ LET IT GO! ♪

420
00:23:06,833 --> 00:23:08,375
- ♪ YOU CAN RUN, YOU CAN STOP,
YOU CAN JUMP, YOU CAN CRAWL ♪

421
00:23:08,458 --> 00:23:10,791
♪ YOU CAN LOSE, YOU CAN WIN ♪

422
00:23:10,875 --> 00:23:13,666
♪ YOU CAN SING, YOU CAN SHOUT
TAKE A BREATH, LET IT OUT ♪

423
00:23:13,750 --> 00:23:16,000
♪ LIVE IT UP EVERY DAY ♪

424
00:23:18,125 --> 00:23:20,500
- Honoka: ASAHINA, I WANTED
TO TALK TO YOU.

425
00:23:20,583 --> 00:23:22,791
YOU SEEM TO BE CLOSE
TO AKITSUKI.

426
00:23:22,875 --> 00:23:25,041
- I WOULDN'T EXACTLY
CALL US CLOSE.

427
00:23:25,125 --> 00:23:27,041
- OH, THEN IS IT OKAY?

428
00:23:27,125 --> 00:23:28,375
- IS WHAT OKAY?

429
00:23:28,458 --> 00:23:31,000
- IS IT OKAY IF I CONFESS
MY FEELINGS TO HIM?

